    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/f078c57e88d77585f90d548982e2f659.poster.avif?t=1728425319\" width=560 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/f078c57e88d77585f90d548982e2f659.webm?t=1728425319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Color Wheels 能帮你轻松选色。这个软件用颜色环的原理，帮你快速找到好看的配色方案。颜色环就是用来展示颜色之间关系的工具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/7a4de89a1411605cd445241be8a7ce1e.poster.avif?t=1728425319\" width=550 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/7a4de89a1411605cd445241be8a7ce1e.webm?t=1728425319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/7a4de89a1411605cd445241be8a7ce1e.mp4?t=1728425319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你只要选个基础颜色，软件就会给你推荐很多漂亮的搭配，让你设计出来的东西看起来更舒服、更协调。你可以选择不同的颜色搭配方式和颜色环类型。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/bbc330e8be32ad0f4310bcd323f3b028.poster.avif?t=1728425319\" width=550 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/bbc330e8be32ad0f4310bcd323f3b028.webm?t=1728425319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/bbc330e8be32ad0f4310bcd323f3b028.mp4?t=1728425319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个软件有很多种颜色环，你可以随意挑选。你可以调整颜色深浅，看看效果。这样就能很快选出你喜欢的颜色组合，用在你的设计上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/299fe3aeac758497f88b99018227ee67.poster.avif?t=1728425319\" width=550 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/299fe3aeac758497f88b99018227ee67.webm?t=1728425319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不管你是做平面设计、网页设计、还是喜欢画画、做视频，这个软件都能帮到你。它能帮你选出最适合的颜色，让你的作品更好看。</p>",
